---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="AI for contractors in Thunder Bay | ThunderBayAI" description="Practical AI opportunities for contractors in Thunder Bay: missed-call recovery, quote follow-up, CRM automation, and cleaner lead flow.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split-panel">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Industry hub</p>
        <h1>AI for contractors in Thunder Bay: where to automate first.</h1>
        <p class="lead">For contractors, the opportunity is not abstract AI. It is faster lead response, better estimate follow-up, cleaner scheduling, and fewer jobs lost because the office side is overloaded.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button" href="/contractor-crm-automation-thunder-bay">See contractor CRM automation</a>
          <a class="button secondary" href="/missed-lead-calculator">Use missed lead calculator</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Top workflow leaks</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>missed calls during active jobs</li>
          <li>slow estimate follow-up</li>
          <li>pipeline visibility gaps</li>
          <li>manual reminder and review requests</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container grid grid-2">
      <a class="card card-link" href="/contractor-crm-automation-thunder-bay"><h3>Contractor CRM automation</h3><p class="muted">The direct implementation path for quote follow-up, lead routing, and pipeline control.</p></a>
      <a class="card card-link" href="/thunder-bay-ai-automation"><h3>Thunder Bay AI automation</h3><p class="muted">Start broader, then narrow into the contractor-specific systems worth installing first.</p></a>
      <a class="card card-link" href="/ai-opportunity-audit"><h3>AI opportunity audit</h3><p class="muted">Use the audit to prioritize the highest-value bottlenecks before adding tools.</p></a>
      <a class="card card-link" href="/missed-lead-calculator"><h3>Missed lead calculator</h3><p class="muted">Turn missed-call and slow-response leakage into a visible number.</p></a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
